# Education-Performance-Resource-Allocation-Dashboard
Interactive Power BI dashboard designed to analyze education performance and resource allocation using data visualization. The dashboard provides insights into student attendance, average marks, pass vs fail distribution, utilization percentage, and resource usage analysis for better academic planning and decision-making.
Project Overview

The Education Performance & Resource Allocation Dashboard is a data visualization project designed to analyze student academic performance, attendance, and institutional resource utilization through interactive charts, KPIs, and reports. This dashboard helps educational institutions monitor learning outcomes, classroom efficiency, and resource management for better academic planning and decision-making.

The project transforms complex educational data into meaningful visual insights, enabling administrators and educators to improve performance tracking and optimize resource allocation.

Key Features
Student Performance Analysis
Subject-wise Average Marks Tracking
Pass vs Fail Distribution Analysis
Attendance Monitoring
Resource Usage & Capacity Analysis
Utilization Percentage by Class
Interactive Charts and KPI Metrics
Student-Teacher Ratio Monitoring
Technologies Used
Power BI
Microsoft Excel
SQL
Data Visualization Techniques
Objective of the Project

The primary goal of this dashboard is to:

Analyze educational performance effectively
Monitor attendance and academic progress
Optimize institutional resource allocation
Support data-driven educational decisions
Visualize performance trends and utilization patterns
Dashboard Insights

The dashboard provides insights into:

Average Student Marks
Subject-wise Performance
Pass & Fail Percentage
Attendance Trends
Resource Utilization Rates
Student-Teacher Ratio
Classroom & Lab Capacity Usage
Overall Academic Performance Status
Use Cases
School Performance Monitoring
College Resource Management
Student Academic Analysis
Attendance & Utilization Reporting
Educational Planning and Decision-Making
